  "detailed_description": "<strong>Why does love always hurt?</strong><br><strong>Why doesn't a good relationship always lead to a happy ending?</strong><br><strong>Does every relationship have a shelf life?</strong><br><strong>Ever felt torn between following your heart and meeting the expectations of others?</strong><br><strong>Why do lovers inevitably have the ultimate battle when they break up?</strong><br><strong>What's the weirdest reason for a breakup you've ever heard?</strong><br><strong>Faced with these unfounded reasons, have you ever had the urge to confront your ex?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/b0074e45fbfa23d18bf8a349c1005c16.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>This game is a Beat 'Em Up with a twist. Unlike traditional beat 'em up arcades where you fight evil bad guys, here, you face off against your ex-lovers. The novelty of the game lies in its rich storytelling, seamlessly blending intense action with deep, emotional plots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Our game allows you to explore and express the intense emotions that arise from intimate conflicts. By the end of your journey, you'll realize that every breakup is less about the other person and more about understanding your own inner self. Reconciling with your past self is a crucial lesson for anyone who has experienced a breakup.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join us in this emotional exploration and find the path to inner peace and understanding through a unique and compelling gameplay experience.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Why does love always hurt?</strong><br><strong>Why doesn't a good relationship always lead to a happy ending?</strong><br><strong>Does every relationship have a shelf life?</strong><br><strong>Ever felt torn between following your heart and meeting the expectations of others?</strong><br><strong>Why do lovers inevitably have the ultimate battle when they break up?</strong><br><strong>What's the weirdest reason for a breakup you've ever heard?</strong><br><strong>Faced with these unfounded reasons, have you ever had the urge to confront your ex?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/b0074e45fbfa23d18bf8a349c1005c16.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>This game is a Beat 'Em Up with a twist. Unlike traditional beat 'em up arcades where you fight evil bad guys, here, you face off against your ex-lovers. The novelty of the game lies in its rich storytelling, seamlessly blending intense action with deep, emotional plots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/25265b189f5326fd67f1aced3a4c5cf7.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/4a473861e74ff7222ed60d72828512f9.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Our game allows you to explore and express the intense emotions that arise from intimate conflicts. By the end of your journey, you'll realize that every breakup is less about the other person and more about understanding your own inner self. Reconciling with your past self is a crucial lesson for anyone who has experienced a breakup.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/8996a05b563e9fe34d6145a0c96d9a31.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.poster.avif?t=1747132074\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.webm?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3020570/extras/1fc707bbd12a20b662b729d663610179.mp4?t=1747132074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join us in this emotional exploration and find the path to inner peace and understanding through a unique and compelling gameplay experience.",
